1.7 Quiz - Editor Overview ✅
# 1. What is the purpose of the Scene dock?
Display all the nodes in the current scene.

#2. Which dock do we use to access the files of our project?
FileSystem

#3. When we select a node, what happens in the Inspector dock?
It displays that node's properties.

1.11 
#1. What is the primary function of the scene viewport in the Godot Editor?
To see and edit the scene from the editor

#2. How do you pan around the screen in 2D mode within the Godot Editor?
Use the middle mouse button

#3. Which of the following assets can be imported into a Godot game project?
Script files
2D textures
Sound file
3D models
All of the above

#4. How do you zoom in and out in the 2D mode of the Godot Editor?
Use the mouse scroll wheel 
